   <pb facs="212"/>
   <head>Bristow to the Reader.</head>
   <p>AL persons of our Nation, that with Gods grace shal chaunce to be remembred or confirmed in the Catholike faith, or reduced thereunto by this Treatise: vouchsafe of theyr charity, to requite my Goodwill, with theyr de<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>uout prayers for my sinnes.</p>
